<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-pt">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GIFWARS - Aguardando Veredito</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body class="p-4 md:p-8">

    {{> header}}

    <span id="room-code-display" class="hidden">{{room.code}}</span>

    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-20 text-center">
        <div class="glass p-16 rounded-[48px] border-t border-white/10 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-purple-600/5 animate-pulse"></div>
            
            <div class="relative z-10">
                <div class="mb-10 flex justify-center">
                    <div class="p-5 bg-purple-500/20 rounded-full shadow-inner animate-bounce">
                        <i data-lucide="award" class="w-16 h-16 text-purple-400"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-4 italic uppercase tracking-tighter">Voto Registado!</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg mb-10 italic">Boa escolha! O júri da Arena está a contar as últimas moedas. Quem será o mestre dos GIFs desta ronda?</p>

                <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6">
                    <div class="flex gap-2">
                        <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-purple-500 rounded-full animate-bounce"></div>
                        <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-purple-500 rounded-full animate-bounce [animation-delay:-0.15s]"></div>
                        <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-purple-500 rounded-full animate-bounce [animation-delay:-0.3s]"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="glass px-8 py-3 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border-white/5">
                        <p class="text-[10px] font-black text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-[0.3em]">Aguardando outros vereditos</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    {{> footer}}

</body>
</html>